29/05/2005
TIRANA, Albania -- President Alfred Moisiu held a series of meetings Friday (27 May), on the pace of preparations for the 3 July parliamentary elections. 
During talks with Local Government Minister Ben Blushi and representatives of the Albanian Mayors' Association, Moisiu urged timely completion of the verification of voters' lists. 
The president also met Friday with Army Chief Lieutenant General Pellumb Qazimi. 
Moisiu stressed that the military command would guarantee no involvement by army members in political activities. 
(Albanian President Web site - 27/05/05)
